title: Pros & Cons of Being on Reality TV!
itunes:title: Pros & Cons of Being on Reality TV!
description:
In this episode, Kimberly Cobb gets deep about how short life is after a recent death in the family, raves about her current faves now that fall is almost here, shares her personal pros & cons from being on reality TV, and more!

 

Follow for weekly episodes of the "My Lips Aren't Sealed" podcast, where I discuss dating, fashion, entertainment, travel, pop culture, and more from my life! Thanks for listening!
